This paper involves using machine learning techniques to predict crime related statistics, specifically crime type in Philadelphia. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
